AI Healthcare App 🏥💡

Empowering Healthcare with AI

Welcome to the official repository of the AI Healthcare App, a project designed to bring artificial intelligence and machine learning into healthcare applications. This app leverages cutting-edge ML models to assist with healthcare-related tasks and provide interactive data-driven insights.

🚀 About Us

Our vision is to make healthcare more accessible, efficient, and insightful through AI. This application demonstrates the potential of AI in healthcare by integrating multiple ML models and visualization tools, aiming to help users understand medical data and predictions in a simple, interactive way.

🌐 Features

AI-Powered Analysis: Uses machine learning models for healthcare predictions and insights.

Interactive Dashboard: Built with Streamlit for user-friendly visualization.

Data Visualization: Integrated with Plotly, Matplotlib, and other tools for interactive charts.

Extensive ML Models: Supports TensorFlow, PyTorch, and other ML libraries.

Multi-Purpose: Can be extended for various healthcare applications like diagnostics, reporting, and monitoring.

🛠️ Tech Stack

Framework: Streamlit

Machine Learning: TensorFlow, PyTorch, scikit-learn, Keras

Data Visualization: Plotly, Matplotlib, Altair

Languages: Python 3.11+

Deployment: Streamlit Cloud, Render, Heroku (recommended)

🚀 Getting Started
Prerequisites

Python 3.11+

Pip package manager

Installation

Clone the repository:

git clone https://github.com/HarshhBansal/Ai-healthcare-app.git
cd Ai-healthcare-app


Create a virtual environment (recommended):

python -m venv healthcare_env
source healthcare_env/bin/activate  # Mac/Linux
.\healthcare_env\Scripts\activate   # Windows


Install dependencies:

pip install -r requirements.txt


Run the app:

streamlit run app.py


Open http://localhost:8501 in your browser to view the app.

📁 Project Structure
Ai-healthcare-app/
├── app.py                  # Main Streamlit application
├── requirements.txt        # Python dependencies
├── runtime.txt             # Runtime info for deployment
└── README.md               # Project description

🎯 Key Functionalities

Data Analysis: Explore healthcare datasets interactively.

Visualization: Generate charts, graphs, and dashboards.

Prediction Models: AI-driven predictions for healthcare scenarios.

Extensible Modules: Add new ML models or analytics tools easily.

